\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5ec9e18 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5ec9e18\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">\u267f\ufe0f Our Commitment to Accessible &amp; Inclusive Web Design<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef6b723 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ef6b723\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"1845\" data-end=\"2048\">Accessibility isn\u2019t a checkbox or trend. It\u2019s a promise. We&#8217;re continuously learning and refining our approach to make sure <strong data-start=\"1969\" data-end=\"1995\">everyone feels welcome<\/strong>, whether you&#8217;re a potential client or just browsing.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-93ff82b elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"93ff82b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b7cc2fc elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b7cc2fc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Compliant. But Always Improving.<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4e7ed0a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4e7ed0a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-535a03b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"535a03b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.w3.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"106\" src=\"https:\/\/hexivox.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/wcag2.1AA-blue-v-300x106.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-2199\" alt=\"wcag2.1AA-blue-v\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hexivox.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/wcag2.1AA-blue-v-300x106.png 300w, https:\/\/hexivox.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/wcag2.1AA-blue-v.png 368w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-255a86c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"255a86c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote><p data-start=\"2095\" data-end=\"2324\"><em data-start=\"2232\" data-end=\"2324\">&#8220;We&#8217;re proud of our 100\/100 Accessibility scores \u2014 and we\u2019re not stopping there.&#8221;<\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bce1fd1 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"bce1fd1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c0a37cf elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c0a37cf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">FAQ<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ed20174 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ed20174\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 data-start=\"289\" data-end=\"344\">\u2753 What does Hexivox mean by &#8220;inclusive web design&#8221;?<\/h4><p data-start=\"345\" data-end=\"553\">Inclusive web design means building websites that are usable by everyone, regardless of ability, device, or neurodiversity. We create experiences that work for real people \u2014 including those with disabilities.<\/p><h4 data-start=\"555\" data-end=\"603\">\u2753 Is your website design WCAG 2.1 compliant?<\/h4><p data-start=\"604\" data-end=\"770\">Yes. We aim to meet or exceed <strong data-start=\"634\" data-end=\"649\">WCAG 2.1 AA<\/strong> standards on every site we build, including keyboard navigation, screen reader compatibility, and clear contrast levels.<\/p><h4 data-start=\"772\" data-end=\"826\">\u2753 Do you test for accessibility?<\/h4><p data-start=\"827\" data-end=\"976\">Yes, we do. With ADHD and epilepsy in our own family, we design with attention filters, sensory sensitivity, and flashing\/animated content safety in mind.<\/p><h4 data-start=\"978\" data-end=\"1035\">\u2753 Can you help make my existing site more accessible?<\/h4><p data-start=\"1036\" data-end=\"1184\">Absolutely. We offer accessibility audits and improvement plans for existing sites to help you comply with standards and better serve your audience.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Accessible &amp; Inclusive Web Design Studio Inclusive Web Design Built for Everyone \u2014 Because We Are Everyone At Hexivox, inclusive web design &amp; accessibility isn\u2019t just a feature \u2014 it\u2019s part of who we are. As a neurodiverse family, we know first-hand how essential it is that digital spaces work for everyone. Between epilepsy, ADHD, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"no-sidebar","site-content-layout":"page-builder","ast-site-content-layout":"full-width-container","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site-post-title":"disabled","ast-breadcrumbs-content":"disabled","ast-featured-img":"disabled","footer-sml-layout":"","theme-transparent-header-meta":"enabled","adv-header-id-meta":"","stick-header-meta":"","header-above-stick-meta":"","header-main-stick-meta":"","header-below-stick-meta":"","astra-migrate-meta-layouts":"set","ast-page-background-enabled":"default","ast-page-background-meta":{"desktop":{"background-color":"","background-image":"","background-repeat":"repeat","background-position":"center center","background-size":"auto","background-attachment":"scroll","background-type":"","background-media":"","overlay-type":"","overlay-color":"","overlay-opacity":"","overlay-gradient":""